{"tid":2416421,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙仲有一個所謂黃絲區議員要清算","createTime":"2021-02-21T04:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T01:58:57.000Z","uid":129471,"like":27,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb07e9dbdb66655d7eecbe9ca3d6a6c05f6c985","tid":2416421,"uid":129471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T04:43:59.000Z","msg":"黃大仙區仲有一個所謂黃絲區議員要清算，果個就係叫自己民主女神、街坊保長既譚香文!!!<br />\n日日話自己黃，但就下下去報狗搞鳩人，跟住又淨係識針對龍蟠苑日日好似小學雞咁去捉人地，(因為佢唔憤氣人地光復左個建制法團之後唔俾光環佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 自己成個選區其他屋苑就咩都唔理，衰到自己做主席既星河明居提都唔提下。<br />\n仲有成個區既居民大部份都俾佢block 左 whatsapp 同 facebook ， Facebook 既留言只要唔岩佢心水，佢就即刻delete 同 block 你。 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2197995/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2197995/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n當然無得唔提佢既代表作發信要求港府幫助滯留武漢孕婦來港產子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1905822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1905822/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VL94y3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VL94y3.png&h=9be058c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一時間係自己Facebook 幫777 宣傳安心不行，俾人屌先換返。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38iOKe2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38iOKe2.jpg&h=987e3cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>成日有外傭聚集，我地就報左警，叫左警察去趕走晒佢地，最後都趕走晒，真係辛苦晒</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mandytamheungman/photos/a.888629141230022/3661410060618569/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmandytamheungman%2Fphotos%2Fa.888629141230022%2F3661410060618569%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvncjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=8c26cb1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mandytamheungman/photos/a.888629141230022/3661410060618569/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/143476022_3661410063951902_4321938297443387682_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=3&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=S6okJATstjcAX-j3Xbg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=47f933acba06d3e35bb709430471a87a&amp;oe=60596471\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F143476022_3661410063951902_4321938297443387682_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26ccb%3D3%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DS6okJATstjcAX-j3Xbg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D47f933acba06d3e35bb709430471a87a%26oe%3D60596471&h=485885ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>頭先有街坊同我哋辦事處講有個著醫院衫嘅人坐咗係龍蟠苑門口🤨，個個經過見到都好擔心，於是我哋就報咗警🧐</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mandytamheungman/photos/pcb.3573659662726943/3573654609394115/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmandytamheungman%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.3573659662726943%2F3573654609394115%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvncjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=7ddfa825\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mandytamheungman/photos/pcb.3573659662726943/3573654609394115/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/132024885_3573654612727448_1860758782195934219_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=3&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=wu-iSUjkdOsAX-Ddp9Y&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=6218c308178e8aaed5bed511c1a631d1&amp;oe=60594257\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F132024885_3573654612727448_1860758782195934219_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26ccb%3D3%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3Dwu-iSUjkdOsAX-Ddp9Y%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D6218c308178e8aaed5bed511c1a631d1%26oe%3D60594257&h=8f920efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我哋明明係善意提醒居民，跟著更有龍蟠苑保安走過嚟滋擾我哋，我哋已經報咗警，同管理公司講，警察已到來我辦事處同我處理！</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mandytamheungman/posts/3534242816668628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmandytamheungman%2Fposts%2F3534242816668628&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvncjT01h1KC